
Add this TXT record to the plusprivacy.com DNS zone.

ian2017._domainkey TXT "v=DKIM1;"

Tell the world that the ONLY mail servers that send mail from this domain are DKIM signed and/or bear our MX and A records.

With SPF:

        SPF "v=spf1 mx a -all"
        TXT "v=spf1 mx a -all"

With DMARC:

_dmarc  TXT "v=DMARC1; p=reject; adkim=s; aspf=r; rua=mailto:dmarc-feedback@plusprivacy.com; ruf=mailto:dmarc-feedback@plusprivacy.com; pct=100"

With DomainKeys (deprecated)

_domainkey TXT "o=-; t=y; r=postmaster@plusprivacy.com"

For more information about DKIM and SPF policy, the documentation within each plugin contains a longer discussion and links to more detailed information:

   haraka -h dkim_sign
   haraka -h spf


